{
  "id": "adv_event_2111_01_02",
  "title": "突撃！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私の両親を招待？\n……ライブに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Invite my parents?\n…To a live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "endTime": 6.666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　新ユニットの結成もあるし\nいい機会なんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We’re forming a new team‚\nso won’t that be a good opportunity?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666666667,
      "endTime": 11.566666666633335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの仕事がいかに尊いものかを知ってもらうには\nそれが一番ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want them to know what a noble job being an idol is‚\nthat’s the best way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7666666667,
      "endTime": 17.299999999966666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……二人とも、何言ってるのよ\n昨日、私の親のこと、話したばかりでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two don’t know what you’re talking about.\nI just told you about my family yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5,
      "endTime": 24.699999999966668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "絶対に来ない\nチケットを無駄にするだけ。無意味よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way they’d come.\nIt would be a waste of tickets. It’s pointless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9,
      "endTime": 29.900000000033334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、怜ちゃんだって\n本当はお父さんに認めてもらいたいんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rei-chan‚ you really want your father to\nacknowledge you‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "endTime": 36.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……別に、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6666666667,
      "endTime": 39.300000000033336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、今、目をそらしましたわね！\n怜、嘘はいけませんわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aha! You can’t meet my eye now!\nRei‚ you mustn’t lie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5,
      "endTime": 44.933333333300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "嘘じゃない\n無駄なことはしたくないだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not lying.\nI just don’t want to waste my time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1333333333,
      "endTime": 48.33333333336667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "意地張ってる感じがするな～\n怜ちゃんらしくないよ。普段はもっと大人なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re being obstinate…\nThat’s not like you at all‚ Rei-chan. You’re normally much more grown up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "endTime": 55.23333333336666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "……だって、今更……もう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no point. It’s already too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4333333333,
      "endTime": 59.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "お父様はともかく、お母様とは連絡を\n取り合っているのでしょう？　お願いすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting your father aside‚ at least you are\nin touch with your mother‚ right? Maybe ask her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8333333333,
      "endTime": 66.30000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "無駄よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s futile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5333333333,
      "endTime": 67.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "なんで分かるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How do you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8666666667,
      "endTime": 69.28666667146837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "……NEXT VENUSグランプリの時\n思い切ってメールしたけど、来てくれなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…At the time of the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nI went ahead and messaged them‚ but they didn’t come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "endTime": 75.39999999996667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……そ、そうでしたの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6,
      "endTime": 78.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、メールしてるってことは\n怜ちゃんもやっぱり本当は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the fact that you messaged them means\nthat Rei-chan do really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9666666667,
      "endTime": 83.40000000003333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "……もういいでしょ、この話は\n私、レッスン行くから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to talk about it anymore.\nI’m going to my lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6,
      "endTime": 88.46666666666665,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5366.666666699999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　怜、まだ話は――\nって、行ってしまいましたわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Rei‚ we’re not done…\nShe left…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6666666667,
      "endTime": 96.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2400.0000000000055
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "思ってた以上にこじれてるみたいだね\n芽衣、怜ちゃんが心配だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s worse than I thought.\nI’m worried about Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.7,
      "endTime": 103.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……私も心配ですけど\n怜のご両親の連絡先も分かりませんのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m worried too.\nWe don’t even know how to contact Rei’s parents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104,
      "endTime": 110.23333333336666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "これ以上、私達に出来ることはありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s nothing more we can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4333333333,
      "endTime": 114.29999999996667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、あるよ\nすずにゃん、行こう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ there is something…\nLet’s go‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5,
      "endTime": 118.60000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "――えっ？　ど、どこに――\nあっ、お待ちなさい！　芽衣！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? W-where to?\nHey‚ wait! Mei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8,
      "endTime": 124.00000000003332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1766.6666667000045
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2400.0000000000055
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 125.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-reidad001.m4a",
      "text": "……私に、君達の――怜のライブを観に来いと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re asking me to go to see Rei's and your live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666666667,
      "endTime": 132.23333333336666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　チケットは用意するので\n怜ちゃんのお母さんとご一緒に！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We’ll arrange the tickets‚\nso please come with Rei-chan's mom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4333333333,
      "endTime": 137.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-reidad002.m4a",
      "text": "……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4666666667,
      "endTime": 138.93333333336665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinose-living",
      "startTime": 139.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "怜のお父様、怖っ！\n……ううっ、まさか怜の実家に乗り込むなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei’s father is scary!\nI can’t believe we just barged into Rei’s parents’ house…",
        "id": ""
      },
